author: Reuters Editorial
title: CBL Properties Reports Q1 Adjusted FFO Per Share $0.42
text:
April 26 (Reuters) - CBL & Associates Properties Inc :
* Q1 ADJUSTED FFO PER SHARE $0.42 * TOTAL PORTFOLIO SAME-CENTER NOI DECLINED 6.8% FOR Q1 2018
* PORTFOLIO OCCUPANCY WAS 91.1% AS OF MARCH 31, 2018, COMPARED WITH 92.1% AS OF MARCH 31, 2017
* SAME-CENTER MALL OCCUPANCY WAS 89.5% AS OF MARCH 31, 2018 COMPARED WITH 90.4% AS OF MARCH 31, 2017
* MAINTAINING 2018 FFO, AS ADJUSTED, GUIDANCE Source text for Eikon:
